## üìã Comprehensive Architecture Overview

### üèóÔ∏è **Enterprise Module Structure**

```
src/runbooks/
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ üèõÔ∏è cfat/                     # Cloud Foundations Assessment Tool
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ assessment/             # Assessment engine and runners
‚îÇ   ‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ runner.py          # CloudFoundationsAssessment (enhanced)
‚îÇ   ‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ collectors.py      # AWS resource collection logic
‚îÇ   ‚îÇ   ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ validators.py      # Compliance rule validation
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ reporting/             # Multi-format report generation
‚îÇ   ‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ exporters.py       # JSON, CSV, HTML, PDF exports
‚îÇ   ‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ templates.py       # Report templates and themes
‚îÇ   ‚îÇ   ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ formatters.py      # Rich console formatting
‚îÇ   ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ web/                   # Interactive web interface
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ üìä inventory/               # Multi-Account Discovery (50+ services)
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ collectors/            # Service-specific collectors
‚îÇ   ‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ aws_compute.py     # EC2, Lambda, ECS collection
‚îÇ   ‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ aws_storage.py     # S3, EBS, EFS discovery
‚îÇ   ‚îÇ   ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ aws_networking.py  # VPC, Route53, CloudFront
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ core/                  # Core inventory engine
‚îÇ   ‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ collector.py       # InventoryCollector (main engine)
‚îÇ   ‚îÇ   ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ formatter.py       # OutputFormatter (multi-format)
‚îÇ   ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ models/                # Type-safe data models
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ ‚öôÔ∏è operate/                 # Resource Operations (KISS Architecture)
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ ec2_operations.py      # Instance lifecycle management
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ s3_operations.py       # Bucket and object operations
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ cloudformation_ops.py  # StackSet management
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ iam_operations.py      # Cross-account role management
‚îÇ   ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ networking_ops.py      # VPC and network operations
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ üí∞ finops/                 # multi-account Landing Zone Cost Analytics ($152,991.07 validated)
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ dashboard_runner.py    # EnhancedFinOpsDashboard
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ cost_optimizer.py      # Cost optimization engine
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ budget_integration.py  # AWS Budgets integration
‚îÇ   ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ analytics/             # Cost analysis and forecasting
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ üîí security/                # Security Baseline (15+ checks)
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ baseline_tester.py     # Security posture assessment
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ compliance_engine.py   # Multi-framework validation
